Fig .9

Then you can assign any created users to any created role (_Chuck_ will remain_ Workflow User Role_ and _Perdo_ will be both_ Workflow User Role_ and _User Defined Role 1_ ). 

!http://forge.taotesting.com/attachments/291/role-assigningUserRole.png!
Fig .9

You can also assign any users to any roles (_Tao Manager 1_ will gain _User Defined Role 1_),

